Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,—Episode 018—\NA promise to Shellenina{NOTE:シェレーニナに誓う}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:00.90,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Oh, what a beautiful ocean.{NOTE:美しい海。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:03.74,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,And such pretty mountains, too.{NOTE:美しい山。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:06.81,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Japan is such a small country, but still so beautiful.{NOTE:この国は小さいけど、美しい国だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:11.80,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Still, I can't get over yesterday's match.{NOTE:それにしても、昨日のあの試合を許せない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:16.36,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara, for some reason I don't want us to part ways like this.{NOTE:鮎原。なぜか私このままあなたと分かれてしまいたくない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:20.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm Ayuhara Kozue.{NOTE:あたしは鮎原こずえです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:24.44,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,I'm the Soviet Union's junior team coach, Rudolph.{NOTE:私はソ連ジュニアチームのコーチ、ルドルフです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:31.35,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,Captain Shellenina wants to speak to you alone.{NOTE:実はキャプテンのシェレーニナは是非あなたと二人きりでお話をしたいと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:34.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Huh? Where is she now?{NOTE:え？シェレーニナ様今どこに？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:36.16,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,She's waiting for you in the pine grove.{NOTE:千本松原で。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:37.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,In the pine grove?{NOTE:千本松原？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:49.47,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What does she want from me? Especially now that I've quit volleyball?{NOTE:バレーを捨てたあたしに、今更一体何よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:52.50,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We don't have anything to discuss.{NOTE:あなたと話し合うことなど何もないはずなのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:54.09,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,And yet…{NOTE:でもあなたのXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:56.17,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Why did you call me over?{NOTE:なぜかあたしをあなたに引かれるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:02:59.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Shellenina-san.{NOTE:シェレーニナさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:03.86,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:06.29,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to trouble you.{NOTE:わざわざ呼び出してごめんなさいね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:12.72,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,But I just wanted to talk to you one more time.{NOTE:どうしてもこのままは分かれたくなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:16.56,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,About the yesterday's game, I mean.{NOTE:皆昨日の試合のせいです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.56,0:03:17.20,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,You won, didn't you. Aren't you satisfied?{NOTE:勝った試合未だ不満があるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.45,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,No.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:22.21,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I'm not satisfied.{NOTE:不満があるのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.66,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Not with me, but with you.{NOTE:それは特にあなたに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:27.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Me? What did I do wrong?{NOTE:私に？あたしが何をしたっと言うの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:29.39,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Your team's playing.{NOTE:日本一富士見学園のプレー。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:31.26,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,It doesn't always have to be about winning or losing.{NOTE:勝敗ぬきで良い試合できる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.95,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I believed in you.{NOTE:あたし信じていました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:36.32,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,But you weren't playing seriously at all.{NOTE:しかし、あなた方真剣でなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.72,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,You forfeited the game right from the start.{NOTE:初めてから試合を捨てていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:39.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong.{NOTE:誤解だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We did our best.{NOTE:あたしたちは一所懸命にだったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.76,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We really did!{NOTE:本当よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.02,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,You were just too good.{NOTE:でもあなたたちはXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,There's a clear difference in our power.{NOTE:実力の差です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We lost because of the skill difference.{NOTE:どうしようもない実力の差で乾杯したんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.95,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Skill?{NOTE:実力？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.10,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Nonsense.{NOTE:とんでもない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.10,0:04:17.87,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I don't think you showed even half of your skill to us.{NOTE:あなた実力も半分を出してなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:21.51,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,You showed us such a splendid game during the All-Japan championships.{NOTE:全日本の決勝戦の時に素晴らしいゲームを見せてくれたのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:24.15,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I refuse to believe that was the full extent of your skill.{NOTE:あれは実力だ何て、私は信じません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:28.00,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:30.77,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Be honest with me.{NOTE:どうか正直に答えてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:34.13,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,What were you thinking about on the court yesterday?{NOTE:昨日あなたはコートで何を考えていたのですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:37.56,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Were you only thinking about victory?{NOTE:私たちの試合に勝つことだけを考えていましたか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.00,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,She's scary.{NOTE:恐ろしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.08,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,She can see right through me.{NOTE:この人は皆見抜いている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.87,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Sensing my weakness flawlessly.{NOTE:あたしの心のXXXも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:51.18,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Rather than focusing on the game, I was thinking about the gym construction and the club's politics.{NOTE:試合の時私はバレーよりも体育館や首位刺々しいしてに心を奪われていた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:52.63,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san?{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:57.28,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Something's troubling you, right? Something big.{NOTE:あなた心の底に何か大きいな悩みがあるですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:05:01.01,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,And that occupied your thoughts during the game, didn't it?{NOTE:そして昨日の試合には別の目的が混じってましたね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:02.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. You're completely right.{NOTE:すみません。その通りです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But how did you know?{NOTE:でもどうしてそれを？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.81,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,We're both volleyball players.{NOTE:同じバレーをやっているもの同士。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:09.60,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,We hit the same ball.{NOTE:一つのボールを打ち合うのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.21,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Of course we understand each other.{NOTE:分からないはず無い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:14.53,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,And after hearing your answer, I'm relieved.{NOTE:でも、あなたの答えを聞いた安心した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:16.11,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,It's just like I thought.{NOTE:私は思った通り。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:19.21,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,You and your team weren't yourselves yesterday.{NOTE:昨日のあなたは本当のあなたじゃなかったのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But I…{NOTE:でも、あたしは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.18,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,What?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:27.26,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It doesn't change anything.{NOTE:このXXX何も話し手も始まらない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:29.56,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's all over anyway.{NOTE:でも皆終わりだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.79,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I quit volleyball, after all.{NOTE:あたしはもうバレーを捨てたんだもん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.21,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:38.23,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,You'll be serious the next time we play, won't you?{NOTE:今度試合する時本当のあなたを打付けれますね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.91,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I'll be looking forward to it.{NOTE:それを期待します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.83,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara, I'm positive…{NOTE:鮎原、あなたはきっと、きっと…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:48.97,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,…that you will become my strongest rival.{NOTE:私の一番恐ろしいライバルに成ると思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:52.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Your rival? Isn't it a bit sudden to decide such a thing?{NOTE:ライバル？そんなこと勝手に決めてもらっては困るだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:55.04,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,You'll surely become my rival.{NOTE:必ずあなたはライバルに成る。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.36,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,And if you don't…{NOTE:もしそうでなかったら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,If I don't…?{NOTE:そうでなかったら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:06:01.06,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you for that game for as long as I live.{NOTE:昨日の試合のこと死ぬまで許しません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:08.52,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Do you understand me now?{NOTE:私の気持ち分かってもらいましたね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:10.36,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes. I understand.{NOTE:え。よく分かりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:12.92,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Thank you.{NOTE:有難う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:16.01,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Please come to Tokyo tomorrow.{NOTE:では、あしたの日曜日東京へ来てください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:18.69,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I want to show you our last game in Japan.{NOTE:日本での最後の試合見てほしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Why?{NOTE:でも、どうして？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.80,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,You'll understand when you see it.{NOTE:見てもらえば分かります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.84,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow in Tokyo.{NOTE:じゃ、あした。東京で。}
