Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.45,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,{NOTE:は！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.48,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,USSR ・ Kitakawa{NOTE:ソ連女子・北川高校男子}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:06.06,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:09.38,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,Our opponents is a high school boys team. You must be surprised.{NOTE:相手は男子高校チームなので、驚いてますね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:13.87,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,But, it'll all make sense soon enough.{NOTE:でもその理由はもうじきあなたにもはっきり分かるはず。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:18.48,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Their opponent is Kitakawa, a high school boys team within the best eight teams in Kantou.{NOTE:相手は高校男子で、然も巻頭のベストエイトに選ばれた北側高校。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:20.53,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,They're far better than the previous opponents.{NOTE:今までよりXXX当然んだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.91,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But, so far, I don't see anything too out of the ordinary.{NOTE:でも別に何も変わってXないじゃないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:26.50,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Is this the game Shellenina wanted to show me?{NOTE:これはシェレーニナはあたしに見せようとしてる試合なのかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:29.47,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,USSR ・ Kitakawa{NOTE:ソ連女子・北川高校男子}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.77,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Nothing has happened.{NOTE:何も起これなかった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:34.59,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Maybe something will in the second set?{NOTE:それとこの第二セットに何が起こるかしら?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:40.94,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,USSR ・ Kitakawa{NOTE:ソ連女子・北川高校男子}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:41.56,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Time.{NOTE:タイム。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.52,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Pinch server, Borchinskaya.{NOTE:ピンチサーバー、ボルチンスカヤ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.40,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Borchinskaya, let's do this just like we practiced.{NOTE:ボルチンスカヤ。練習通りにやるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:08.98,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,Borchinskaya hasn't been in any of the official matches because of her inability to stand upright.{NOTE:あの選手はまだ(X・起立)が不足のため公式試合には出したことがありません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:12.32,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,But she's under Shellenina's strict training as her secret weapon.{NOTE:今シェレーニナは特訓中の秘密兵器なのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What do you mean?{NOTE:それと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.82,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Take your pace.{NOTE:思い切ってやりなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.74,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Nothing happened during that serve.{NOTE:サーブでは何も起こらない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:28.46,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Does Borchinskaya's power manifest in the attack?{NOTE:とうすれば、ボルチンスカヤはアタック攻撃に回った特に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:31.44,Blackboard,,0,0,0,,USSR ・ Kitakawa{NOTE:ソ連女子・北川高校男子}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.30,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Borchinskaya's finally on the attacking position.{NOTE:いよいよボルチンスカヤはXXX回って来た。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:39.87,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That must be it.{NOTE:ここだわ、きっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.86,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Strange. It was still pretty ordinary.{NOTE:可笑しい。こんなはずはないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:09:01.36,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What exactly did Shellenina want to show me?{NOTE:シェレーニナはあたしに何を見せるつもりなんだろう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:04.73,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san. You seem disappointed.{NOTE:鮎原さん。拍子抜けなさってますね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.56,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,Let me give you a hint.{NOTE:ヒントを言いましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:10.86,Default,Rudolph,0,0,0,,Pay attention when Shellenina gets in the center.{NOTE:シェレーニナはセンターに入った時に気をつけてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.30,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,In the center?{NOTE:センターに？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.96,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Chance ball!{NOTE:チャンスボール。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.25,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:お！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:42.30,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– What's wrong?\N– Hey, what's wrong?{NOTE:—どうした？\\N—おい、どうした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:44.30,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Are you hurt?\N– You okay?{NOTE:—どうした？\\N—X、どうした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.87,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,My hand. My hand…!{NOTE:手、手が。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.41,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Should I call for help?{NOTE:大丈夫か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:52.17,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What a destructive power.{NOTE:あの攻撃、すごい破壊力。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:55.15,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Shellenina, you really are a scary person.{NOTE:シェレーニナ、あなたは恐ろしい人だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:59.04,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That must be devastating. There was no defending that.{NOTE:あ、悪夢だは、きっと。こんな試合は言い訳が無い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:01.73,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:06.05,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,How was it? Do you get it now? Why I wanted to show you our game?{NOTE:どうでした？この試合をあなたに見てもらった理由が分かりましたか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:13.34,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,I want to reignite the Japanese attacker's passion within you.{NOTE:あなたに早く日本人のアタッカーの情熱のファイト取り戻してほしいのです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:18.72,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Borchinskaya can't use her right leg very well.{NOTE:このボルチンスカヤ右足不自由んです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.72,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,She hurt it when she was little.{NOTE:小さい時XXしました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.35,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,In volleyball, one needs a good jump the most.{NOTE:バレーにはジャンプ一番必要なのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.95,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,But even though she can't jump that high…{NOTE:そのジャンプ力は普通の人の半分もない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:31.44,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Borchinskaya still wants to play no matter what.{NOTE:でもボルチンスカヤどしてもバレーがやりたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:36.85,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,That is why she and I thought of our own technique: the "cross toss".{NOTE:それで彼女とわたくし二人で考え出したのは十字トスです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.31,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Cross toss…?{NOTE:十字トス？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:40.16,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Yes. A cross toss.{NOTE:そう。十字トス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:44.24,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,It happens when Borchinskaya hits the ball low.{NOTE:ボルチンスカヤのアタック低いXXと打ちます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:48.71,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,That's why I need to make it powerful with a curve ball.{NOTE:だから、変化球で破壊力をつけなければならない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:53.03,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,When I'm in the center, I give rotation to the ball and pass it to her.{NOTE:そこで私センターに入ってトスボールに回転を当たれ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:57.94,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Borchinskaya accepts it and hits it with even stronger force.{NOTE:ボルチンスカヤはそれをさらに強い力で変化させます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.64,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san. I'm going back to Russia.{NOTE:鮎原さん。あたしは国へ変える。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:04.35,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,There, I'll train cross toss and Borchinskaya even more.{NOTE:十字トスとボルチンスカヤもさらに、さらに鍛えます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.76,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,And I'll also be waiting for your letter of challenge.{NOTE:そしてあなたの挑戦を待っています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:08.56,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Very well, Shellenina-san.{NOTE:え。いいわ、シェレーニナさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.03,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,When we meet again…{NOTE:今度のお会いする時…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.46,Default,Shellenina,0,0,0,,…let's meet on the court. Farewell.{NOTE:必ずコートで。さようなら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Good bye.{NOTE:さようなら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:26.00,Alternative,Shellenina,0,0,0,,"There, I'll train cross toss and Borchinskaya even more."{NOTE:あたしは十字トスとボルチンスカヤを更に鍛えます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:29.01,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,"And I'll also be waiting for your letter of challenge."{NOTE:そしてあなたの挑戦を待っています。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.23,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Shellenina.{NOTE:シェレーニナ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.54,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I understood something.{NOTE:おかげで一つをはっきりしたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.92,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I can't go on without volleyball.{NOTE:あたしはバレー無では生きていけないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:39.08,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I have to return to volleyball… To our club.{NOTE:あたしはバレー部に帰る。バレー部へ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.60,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:43.29,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:43.92,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Here I go!{NOTE:行くわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.92,0:11:44.64,Default,Ikezaki,0,0,0,,Roger.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:45.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:46.80,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:47.66,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:49.20,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Once more.{NOTE:もういっぽん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.44,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,All right.{NOTE:よいっしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:52.88,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,I thought Ayuhara-san quit volleyball?{NOTE:あら？鮎原さんはバレーをやるXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.09,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,I guess it was just a rumor.{NOTE:嘘だったのかしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.52,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Of course it was.{NOTE:嘘も決まってるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:59.30,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,There is no Ayuhara Kozue without volleyball.{NOTE:鮎原とXXバレーXX考えられないもう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:00.16,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Again!{NOTE:もういっぽん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:00.74,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Come on!{NOTE:おう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:01.33,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Here!{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:03.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:08.83,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah.{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.02,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,I want to talk to you for a bit.{NOTE:君にちょっと話がある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.42,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you on the shrine's premises.{NOTE:神社の境内へ待っているよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oh.{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Tsutomu-kun!{NOTE:努くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:22.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What exactly did you want to talk about? I need to go back to practice soon.{NOTE:ね、話して何よ。あたし今XX練習したいの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:23.59,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Well?{NOTE:ね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:24.73,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,It's just…{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:27.00,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,I thought you had quit volleyball?{NOTE:君はバレー部を止めたんじゃなかったのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:30.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Whether I quit or not has nothing to do with you, now does it?{NOTE:そんなこと努くんに何も関係ないことでしょう？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:32.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'll keep playing volleyball no matter what people think.{NOTE:誰がどう思うとあたしはバレーをやるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:36.48,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Hmph. Then you'll wave the championship pennant again?{NOTE:フン。そしてもう一度優勝旗を振り回そうって言うのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:40.11,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No, I don't have such a small goal anymore.{NOTE:お生憎様。あたしはそんなちっちゃなことを狙ってないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,The Soviet Union's captain, Shellenina, is my rival now.{NOTE:あたしの敵はソ連のシェレーニナよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:44.04,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Shellenina?{NOTE:シェレーニナ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:47.04,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Kozue-kun, you still don't get it, do you?{NOTE:こずえくん。君はやっぱり分かってないんだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Say what you want.{NOTE:なんとでもおっしゃい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I made a promise to Shellenina-san.{NOTE:シェレーニナさんと約束したのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:53.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,When we meet again, my team will win for sure.{NOTE:今度会う時にかならず勝つって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.12,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Win?{NOTE:勝つ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.11,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Oh, how sweet.{NOTE:立派だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.77,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,I see that the volleyball club's goal is still just to win.{NOTE:バレーの目的はただ勝つことにXXXね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.27,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Knock it off!{NOTE:もう止めて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:03.34,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,You don't understand me at all, do you?{NOTE:努くん何かにはあたしの今の気持ちが分かってたまるもんですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.55,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Kozue-kun.{NOTE:こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:努くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:09.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,You'd be overjoyed if I quit volleyball, wouldn't you?{NOTE:あなたはあたしがバレー部を止めればいいと思ってるのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:10.07,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,What?{NOTE:何だって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:11.30,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I get it.{NOTE:分かってるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:16.96,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,If I quit our club… you wouldn't have to oppose building of the new gym anymore.{NOTE:あたしがバレー部を止めれば、そうすれば、もうバレー部専用の体育館を建てるなんて言わないと思って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.12,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,You idiot!{NOTE:バカ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:20.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess I am an idiot!{NOTE:え。どうせあたしはバカよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:21.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,So leave this idiot alone.{NOTE:放っといて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.75,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Kozue-kun!{NOTE:こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:24.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Let go of me!{NOTE:何よ、放してよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:26.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What I do is none of your business!{NOTE:あなたに何か関係ないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:27.89,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,What did you say?{NOTE:何だと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:29.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:36.93,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,You… you're only…{NOTE:君は自分が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:38.74,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Hey, Ichinose.{NOTE:待てよ、一ノ瀬。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:42.38,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Don't lay a hand on Ayuhara-kun.{NOTE:せっかくはりきってる鮎原くんをケチを付けるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.96,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,What's so wrong about winning in sports?{NOTE:スポーツ(XX・漫画)試合に勝って、何が悪いんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:48.92,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,What the hell do you know about any of this?{NOTE:第一スポーツもやったこともない貴様何かに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:51.51,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,You think you're in any position to preach to Ayuhara-kun?{NOTE:…鮎原くんをせめるしかくがあると思ってるのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:54.40,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,I'm not preaching to her.{NOTE:三田村、僕は責めるんじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:56.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,I'm just worried about her.{NOTE:僕はこずえのこと心配してるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.48,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Tch, you bastard.{NOTE:チェ。このやろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.79,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Bring it on.{NOTE:やろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.00,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Now you did it.{NOTE:やったな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:06.72,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Fight back, you coward.{NOTE:えい。卑怯だ。この。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:07.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Stop it.{NOTE:止めて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:08.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I said, stop it!{NOTE:止めてよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Stop it right now, you two!{NOTE:止めてったら、二人共。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:14.29,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,If you have to fight, take it someplace where I can't see it.{NOTE:喧嘩するなら、あたしの見てない所でやってちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.63,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Your fight is an eyesore.{NOTE:迷惑だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:19.23,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thank you for worrying about me.{NOTE:あたしのこと心配してくれるのありがたいけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:22.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But you don't understand anything at all.{NOTE:あなたたち何も、何も分かっちゃいないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:24.03,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,But I do understand you.{NOTE:そんな。ばかな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:25.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No, you don't.{NOTE:いいえ。そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:28.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'll be doing what I want regardless of what either of you say.{NOTE:あなたたちがどう思うと、あたしはやりたいことをやるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:34.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Don't interfere with my life anymore.{NOTE:だからもう二度とあたしのこと口出ししないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Goodbye.{NOTE:さようなら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:46.01,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\t(0,459,\alpha&HFF&)\t(459,1877,\alpha&H00&)}Ayuhara family{NOTE:鮎原}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.24,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:55.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:21.50,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,"What are you playing volleyball for?"{NOTE:君たちは何のためにバレーをやっているんだ?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:23.50,Alternative,Hongou,0,0,0,,"Ayuhara. You first."{NOTE:鮎原。答えろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:32.68,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,"The volleyball club's goal is still just to win."{NOTE:バレーのも目的はただ勝つことなのさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.76,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's right.{NOTE:そうよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:36.73,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'll win against Shellenina.{NOTE:シェレーニナにはあたしは勝つ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:38.46,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'll win, for sure.{NOTE:絶対に勝つわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.29,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No matter what anyone says.{NOTE:例え誰が何と言おうと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:42.99,Alternative,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.58,Alternative,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,It seems you're unable to focus on your true goals now.{NOTE:お前は自分の方針から目を背け落としている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.34,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,Kozue.{NOTE:こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:48.03,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Hm?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome back, papa.{NOTE:あら、おかえりなさい、パパ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.26,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,I want to show you something.{NOTE:お前に見せたい物がある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:53.88,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,Come to my room.{NOTE:パパの部屋へお出で。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.82,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What does he want to show me?{NOTE:見せたい物？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:01.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What's this?{NOTE:え？なに、これ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.02,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,It's a German dictionary.{NOTE:ドイツ語の辞書だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.50,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,German?{NOTE:ドイツ語の？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:08.87,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– But it has no contents?\N– I tore out the pages and threw them away.{NOTE:—あら、中身がないわ。\\N—破って捨てたさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.26,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Why would you do that?{NOTE:破って？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.88,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,It's a story from my days as a student.{NOTE:パパが学生のころの話だが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:17.09,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,I wanted to remember all of the words inside.{NOTE:この辞書に乗っている単語全部覚えてやろうと決心したんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:23.39,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,But remembering five hundred pages worth of words is no small feat.{NOTE:所が五百ページもある単語を覚えると言うとはそれは並大抵のことじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.46,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,Still, I focused really hard.{NOTE:そこで色々と考えたXX…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.09,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,Each time I finished remembering a\hpage, I tore it out and threw it away.{NOTE:一ページ覚えるの時に、そのページを破り捨てたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:36.65,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,And when I'd torn the last page…{NOTE:そして、最後の一ページを破り捨てた時は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:38.97,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,…It felt like I had conquered the world.{NOTE:世界を征服したなような気分だったよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:45.23,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,This dictionary without pages has been my treasure ever since.{NOTE:それ以来このページのない辞書はパパの宝に成ったんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:48.29,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,Do you see what I'm getting at, Kozue?{NOTE:分かるか、こずえ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:51.19,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,It's about having the courage to confront the impossible.{NOTE:人のできないことに、全力をかけて、ぶつかっていく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:53.02,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,Isn't that what youth is all about?{NOTE:それが青春と言うものじゃないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:58.83,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,Even if it ends with failure, you should approach your goals with full power.{NOTE:例えそれは失敗に終わっても目的に向かって最後まで我武者羅にぶつかっていく。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:01.83,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,What matters the most is having a positive attitude.{NOTE:大切なのは前向きな姿勢じゃないかと思ったからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.71,0:17:05.20,Default,Ayuhara's dad,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kozue?{NOTE:どうした、こずえ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:08.00,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Papa, I think I understand.{NOTE:パパ、あたしは分かってるのような気がするの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:14.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Professor, I understand it now.{NOTE:先生、あたしは分かったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:15.52,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Hm?{NOTE:ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:20.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I know the answer to your question about why we're playing volleyball.{NOTE:先生のおっしゃった、何のためにバレーをやるかが分かったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,All right, let's hear it.{NOTE:聞こう。言ってご覧。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:27.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It seems that we forgot something important in the craze of winning the championships.{NOTE:あたしたち優勝することばかり考えて感じが大事なことを忘れていたようです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:35.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I can't quite find the words, but… I think we should've been aiming for something else.{NOTE:口ではうまく言えませんけど、優勝のそのまた先にある何か私たちは目指さなければいけなかったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:40.28,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Winning was the reason we practice so hard. We pushed our bodies to their limits.{NOTE:そのために厳しい練習もうし、人間の限界まで挑戦する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.38,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,That's right.{NOTE:そうだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:44.55,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,And victories are the compensation for that hard work.{NOTE:そして、その動力の代償は優勝なんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.55,0:17:49.24,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,People keep saying "victory, victory". But the moment you win, it becomes the glory of the past.{NOTE:人は優勝、優勝とさないけど勝った瞬間それはもう過去の栄光にしか過ぎない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.24,0:17:53.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What's important is to aim for one's own goals and maintain a positive attitude.{NOTE:大切なことは狙いに向かってぶつかっていく心構え。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.04,0:17:54.73,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, professor?{NOTE:そうでしょう、先生？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:56.46,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Exactly.{NOTE:その通り。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:57.72,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,But Ayuhara…{NOTE:しかし、鮎原。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:01.45,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Did you really come to this realization by yourself?{NOTE:それほどのこと、君一人で考えついたと思えないが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:03.85,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Well, my dad helped me.{NOTE:え。実は、父に。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:05.56,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Oh? You've got a good father.{NOTE:お？良いお父さんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.06,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're one happy girl.{NOTE:君は幸せものだぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I am.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.86,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Then there's you, Shellenina.{NOTE:そしてもう一人シェレーニナ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:12.56,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Shellenina, I finally understand.{NOTE:シェレーニナ、今私には分かる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:14.81,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Your kindhearted strength…{NOTE:あなたの力強い思いやりが。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:20.27,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It showed me that I can't possibly escape the world of volleyball.{NOTE:あたしはもう見えない。この少し(XXX・奥深い)バレーの世界からもう逃げることはできない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:23.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:24.94,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:27.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:29.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:それ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:31.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:34.60,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Whoa, awesome.{NOTE:あ、すごい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.64,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Our chief sure looks different today.{NOTE:今日の親分何だXXX見たい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:39.40,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Of course she does. She actually looks happy for a change.{NOTE:それはそうよ。XXX近づいたんですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:41.35,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It's only natural. Right, Kozue?{NOTE:当然よ。ね、こずえ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yeah. But make no mistake, girls.{NOTE:え。でも皆誤解しないでね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:48.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Winning the autumn's All-Japan championships isn't the only thing on my mind anymore.{NOTE:もうあたしは秋の全国大会でただ優勝すれば良いとだけと思ってるわけじゃないんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.12,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I have another objective.{NOTE:目的が別にあるの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:53.79,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Really? Because I intended to make winning this championship my primary objective.{NOTE:あら？あたしは優勝第一目的やってるつもりだけど？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:56.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Winning this, winning that. That mindset will get us nowhere.{NOTE:ただ優勝、優勝って、あまり優勝に拘れと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:59.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It'll just leave us in a hole that we can't climb out of.{NOTE:大きな落とし穴に落ちるといけないと思って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.06,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,A hole?{NOTE:落とし穴？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:01.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yep.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:07.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,The road we travel will be full of holes. But for our club, the end of that road is nowhere in sight.{NOTE:どん詰まりの前には必ず落とし穴があるけど、 私たちのバレー部は突き当たりがないのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.05,0:19:08.19,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,Hey, Naka.{NOTE:ね、ナカ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:12.19,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,I hope that the other clubs will come to understand our feelings.{NOTE:あたしたちのこの気持ちが 他の部の人たちにも 分かってもらえるといいんだけどね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.68,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Me too. If they do…{NOTE:うん。そうすればさ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:18.19,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,…there will be no one to oppose building a new gym for us.{NOTE:…バレー部専用体育館の建設に 繁体する人もいなくなるのにね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:20.01,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,How about we give up on that?{NOTE:それはもう諦めましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:24.22,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We have no right to ask for a new gym after losing to the Soviet Union.{NOTE:ソ連チームに負けた以上、あたしたち そんなXXX出す資格はないですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:28.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,0)}Club meeting{NOTE:クラブ機会\\N会議中}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:36.08,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,We will now resume the debate about the construction of a gym for the volleyball club.{NOTE:では前回からの持ち越し 時代である バレー部専用の体育館建設について 会議を開きます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:38.48,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,If you have an opinion, go ahead and speak.{NOTE:意見がある方はどうぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:39.44,Default,Nozawa,0,0,0,,I do.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Before that, please hear me out.{NOTE:その前にあたしから一言言わせてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:43.44,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:47.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Please withdraw the construction.{NOTE:体育館の問題を取り下げてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.14,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:51.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Just like Nozawa-san and Ichinose-san said…{NOTE:あたしたち、野沢さんと一ノ瀬さん言われた通り…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:53.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,…we will practice outdoors from now on.{NOTE:…今後は外で練習することにします。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:54.55,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's all.{NOTE:それだけです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:57.53,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Huh?\N– What's the meaning of this?{NOTE:え？一体どう言うことなの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:59.98,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– How surprising.\N– I never expected that from her.{NOTE:—飽きれたね。\\N—そんなにXXくせにね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:04.82,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Excuse me. I have a question for Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:ちょっと。鮎原くんに質問があります。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:05.83,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,Go ahead.{NOTE:どうぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.47,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Why the sudden change of heart?{NOTE:なぜそんなに急にこの問題を取り下げちゃったんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:13.27,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Did you forget that some of us already agreed to it?{NOTE:体育館の建設には賛成もあるってこと忘れずに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:18.93,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's just… we can play volleyball pretty much anywhere.{NOTE:でもあたしたちはバレーさえ出来れば どこでもよかったんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:22.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We were wrong to demand such a privilege.{NOTE:立派な練習XXXあたしたちの間違いでした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:26.76,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Chairman. I agree to the construction.{NOTE:議長。僕も体育館の建設に賛成です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:28.76,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Eh?\N– That was unexpected.{NOTE:—え？\\N—変ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.76,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,How could you betray us?{NOTE:あんた、裏切り者よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.92,0:20:34.70,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,Settle down. Ichinose-kun, go on.{NOTE:XXX。一ノ瀬くん続けてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:37.05,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Sure, up until now I've opposed the construction.{NOTE:この間まで僕は反対でした。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.47,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,"We can't practice without a gym of our own."{NOTE:専用の体育館がなければ、練習できないとか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.69,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,"We won an All-Japan tournament, so give us money."{NOTE:全国大会に優勝したんだから、XXXとか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:44.90,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,If the volleyball club had continued with that attitude, I'd still oppose it.{NOTE:そう言うバレー部のようきょうだったら、 今でも僕は反対です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:46.70,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,But now, Ayuhara-kun…{NOTE:でも今、鮎原くんは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.84,Alternative,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Ichinose, what are you trying to say?{NOTE:一ノ瀬、お前一体何を言いたいんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:51.52,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,…says she doesn't need the gym anymore.{NOTE:もう体育館をいらないと言いました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:55.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,I think that for the first time we heard from our volleyball club's captain…{NOTE:このキャプテンの声で初めて 我が富士見学園バレー部は}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.51,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,…saying that her club is qualified to have its own gym.{NOTE:専用の体育館を持つ資格を持ったんだと僕は思うんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:01.47,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Her love for the club is so pure.{NOTE:バレー部を浄水に愛するからこそ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Same goes for her love for sports.{NOTE:スポーツを愛するからこそ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.15,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,So much that she doesn't need anything else.{NOTE:今は何もいらないと時代した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:10.58,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,So that's why I think we should agree to the construction of a new gym—{NOTE:そのバレー部のために 僕たちはなんとか 体育館建設を実現させて—}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.95,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,That's right!{NOTE:そうだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.67,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,It's just like Ichinose says.{NOTE:一ノ瀬の言う通りだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.67,0:21:17.25,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,It's a shame for us to say there's no place for them to practice…{NOTE:我だが富士見学園の名を天下に轟くしてくれたバレー部に}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:21.64,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,…to the team that roared our school's name to the world.{NOTE:専用の練習場もないと言うこと 我々前向性との恥だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:22.35,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Yeah!{NOTE:そうだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.85,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Nice, Mitamura!{NOTE:いいぞ、三田村。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.70,0:21:26.97,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tsutomu-kun, Mitamura-san.{NOTE:ありがとう、努くん。三田村さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:29.20,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,What's everyone else's opinion?{NOTE:皆さん、どうですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.85,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Agreed!\N– Nobody opposes?{NOTE:—賛成。—賛成。\\N—XXあるかたはありませんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:34.61,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,Then it is an unanimous decision.{NOTE:あ、では全員一で賛成と認めます。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:38.77,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,Very well.{NOTE:よろしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:46.37,Default,Principal,0,0,0,,The final decision on the volleyball club's very own gym will be reviewed at the next staff meeting.{NOTE:ではバレー部専用体育館建設の件は 職員会議にかけたうえ 正式に決定します。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:50.07,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Tsutomu-kun, thank you very much.{NOTE:努くん、どうも有難う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:51.58,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,You too, Mitamura-san.{NOTE:それから三田村さんも。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:54.51,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Today I saw a new side of Ichinose.{NOTE:うん。俺今日は一ノ瀬を見直したよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:56.76,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,You can say nice things once in a while.{NOTE:お前いいことを言うな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:21:58.27,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Let's shake on it.{NOTE:おい、握手しよう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:21:59.48,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,Yep. However…{NOTE:ん。しかし…}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:02.34,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,It doesn't change that Mitamura and I are rivals.{NOTE:三田村と僕とはライバルとあることは変えないぜ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:06.27,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,Hm? Y-Yeah. Sure.{NOTE:ん？あ、あ。いいぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.27,0:22:07.71,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Hahahaha.{NOTE:ハハハハ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:10.49,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,This is a great honor to us.{NOTE:我々としては一応喜ぶべきことだが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:13.58,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,But it also leaves heavier responsibilities.{NOTE:…それだけに責任はますます重くなるわけだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:16.44,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,The next All-Japan championship is right around the corner.{NOTE:え、差し当たり目前に迫っている全国大会だが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:20.90,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,So the upcoming practices will focus on that tournament.{NOTE:今後の練習スケジュールは全て この大会に焦点を合わせることにする。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:24.94,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,From now on, I will have Ayuhara lead the way.{NOTE:これからはほとんどのことを 鮎原にやってもらうことにするから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.94,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I'd like you all to listen to her.{NOTE:皆もそのつもりでいってもらいたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:30.18,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I'm sure Ayuhara can handle it.{NOTE:鮎原ならそれが出きるはずだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:33.17,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Treat her orders as if they were mine.{NOTE:諸君もキャプテンの言うこと 私の言うことだと思って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:35.33,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,I want you all to train hard.{NOTE:練習に励んでほしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:36.47,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Understood?{NOTE:いいな？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.47,0:22:37.99,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Yes sir!\N– Yes sir!{NOTE:—はい！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:40.25,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,All right. That's it for today.{NOTE:よし。それじゃ、今日はここで解散する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:43.03,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,The captain will decide the schedule from tomorrow.{NOTE:明日からのスケジュールはキャプテンが決めろ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.03,0:22:44.31,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Got it, Ayuhara?{NOTE:いいな、鮎原？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:44.94,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes sir.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:47.21,Default,Hongou,0,0,0,,Dismissed.{NOTE:では、解散。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:51.73,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue, take it easy.{NOTE:こずえ、お手やらかにね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:53.35,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Midori, you'll help me out, right?{NOTE:うん。みどり、助けてね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:56.18,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I don't think I can do it alone.{NOTE:私一人でとっても 心細くって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:57.38,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.{NOTE:なに言ってるの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.38,0:22:59.46,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,You will do just fine.{NOTE:あなたなら十分やれるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:04.13,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,Exactly. Practicing with Ayuhara-san will be much more fun than with professor Hongou.{NOTE:そうよ。鮎原さんならさ、本郷先生と間違った楽しさで練習できるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:05.59,Default,Kashiwagi,0,0,0,,This really is great news.{NOTE:とにかく、いいことよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:06.24,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,That's right.{NOTE:本当。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:09.21,Default,Nakazawa,0,0,0,,Professor Hongou will be shocked with the results.{NOTE:本郷先生XXXじゃん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:13.97,Default,Ikezaki,0,0,0,,But what's he planning to do by leaving coaching to you?{NOTE:でもコーチをあなたに任せて 本号先生は何をする気かしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.97,0:23:16.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'm sure he has his motives.{NOTE:きっと作戦に(XX・せんけん・せんげん)するつもりよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:19.82,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,It reminds me of the "strategy without strategy".{NOTE:又「作戦無き作戦」何てこと考え出すかもよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:20.78,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.78,0:23:21.52,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Yes?{NOTE:はい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:24.13,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,There's a letter for you.{NOTE:あ、あなたに手紙だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:25.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Eh? Where from?{NOTE:え？あたしに？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:26.76,Sign,,0,0,0,,Fukuoka Middle School\NKakinouchi Yoshiko{NOTE:福岡中学内\\N垣之内良子}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.31,0:23:30.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's from Kakinouchi-san at Fukuoka's Middle School.{NOTE:ま、福岡中学の垣之内さんからだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:31.44,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,Huh?{NOTE:へ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.44,0:23:33.13,Default,Kudou,0,0,0,,What did she write?{NOTE:何であの人から？}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:36.09,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Oh…{NOTE:ま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.09,0:23:37.65,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's a letter of challenge.{NOTE:挑戦状だわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.55,0:23:42.13,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,All right, Shellenina.{NOTE:そうだ、シェレーニナ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.13,0:23:46.03,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,There is someone else I need to fight before we battle each other.{NOTE:あなたと戦う前に、もう一人戦わなければならない人がいったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.69,0:23:56.43,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Kakinouchi of Fukuoka Middle School delivers a letter of challenge.{NOTE:福岡中学垣之内良子自信に満ちた挑戦状。}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.43,0:24:01.55,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Kozue makes a promise to coach Hongou to fight with a new strength.{NOTE:こずえは本号コーチに誓う： 「こちらも新しい力で戦うのみだ」。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.55,0:24:06.03,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Midori suggests spending summer vacation camping in Karuizawa, but Kozue rejects it.{NOTE:こずえは夏休みの合宿 軽井沢でと言う みどりの提案もXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.03,0:24:08.60,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Instead, she wants to hold strict training sessions every day.{NOTE:連日厳しくトレーニングを指導する。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.60,0:24:14.92,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,And the girls aren't thrilled with the severity of Kozue's training, including Kashiwagi and Midori.{NOTE:だが、そんなこずえにXX みどりやかしわぎ以下 部員の間に だんだん 反感が詰まっている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.92,0:24:17.32,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,And so, a rebellion arises!{NOTE:そしてついにXXXは爆発した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:21.08,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.{NOTE:さ、来週のアタックナンバーワンをお楽しみに。}
